Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}要有...大事...发生了  你们哪！\N{\fs40\b0}It... is... going... downtown, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:49.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我考虑好了  我两个都要\N{\fs40\b0}I've thought on it... and I choose both.
