Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.90,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你真是个“好”伙计  - 我更喜欢你叫我“超级好”的伙计\N{\fs40\b0}- You're a good friend. - I would've gone with "great."
